112
00:10:37,980 --> 00:10:38,990
Please enjoy it.

113
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:22,990
I have a meeting at 8:30 a.m.,

114
00:11:22,990 --> 00:11:24,320
and you'll come with me.

115
00:11:24,570 --> 00:11:25,850
It's Saturday.

116
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,910
Except for workdays,

117
00:11:27,930 --> 00:11:29,280
