124
00:11:39,070 --> 00:11:40,130
Thank you, master.

125
00:11:56,110 --> 00:11:56,920
Chen Jun,

126
00:11:57,500 --> 00:11:58,830
come with me in a minute.

127
00:11:59,090 --> 00:11:59,660
Where?

128
00:12:00,190 --> 00:12:00,750
Mr. Zhou,

129
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:01,730
