134
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:17,550
but

135
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:19,960
I still hope you can keep it a secret for me.

136
00:12:20,870 --> 00:12:21,600
Don't worry,

137
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:23,030
I won't put you in danger.

138
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:31,150
Thank you.

139
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:32,300
Mr. Zhou,

140
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:34,120
