167
00:13:42,590 --> 00:13:43,490
Thank you, big sister.

168
00:13:43,490 --> 00:13:44,420
You're welcome.

169
00:13:45,610 --> 00:13:46,200
She's a good girl.

170
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:46,730
Let's go.

171
00:13:51,060 --> 00:13:51,640
Here.

172
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:52,380
Little girl,

173
00:13:52,380 --> 00:13:52,980
take this.

174
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:54,050
Thank you.

175
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:54,830
Bye.

176
00:14:11,830 --> 00:14:12,640
Thank you.

177
00:14:15,230 --> 00:14:17,020
