181
00:14:27,430 --> 00:14:29,030
You think I'll listen to you?

182
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:31,030
No.

183
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:45,050
Hurry up.

184
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:46,800
I've tried my best.

185
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:50,490
We're in the opposite direction.

186
00:14:50,490 --> 00:14:51,200
Go back.

187
00:14:51,830 --> 00:14:52,550
No, I mean that way.

188
00:14:52,550 --> 00:14:53,210
Over there.

189
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:55,580
Hurry up.

190
00:14:58,710 --> 00:14:59,160
You keep an eye on them.

191
00:14:59,160 --> 00:14:59,930
