194
00:15:09,620 --> 00:15:10,950
This is really good.

195
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,210
I'm glad you like it.

196
00:15:12,420 --> 00:15:14,270
They bought a lot of snacks,

197
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:16,080
with food and drinks,

198
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:17,020
and...

199
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:18,560
