207
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:35,210
Go head.

208
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,190
Are you tired?

209
00:15:45,190 --> 00:15:46,140
Do you need me to pedal?

210
00:15:46,140 --> 00:15:46,710
I'm not tired

211
00:15:46,710 --> 00:15:47,730
