212
00:15:47,730 --> 00:15:49,530
Could you get me a glass of water?

213
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,590
She opened a bottle of beverage,

214
00:15:51,590 --> 00:15:52,550
and...

215
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,510
and they leaned together.

216
00:15:56,940 --> 00:15:57,940
Leaned together?

217
00:15:58,280 --> 00:15:59,570
L-Leaned together.

218
00:15:59,860 --> 00:16:00,660
How?

219
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,410
