245
00:16:54,570 --> 00:16:55,160
Let's sit here.

246
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:55,770
Okay.

247
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:57,510
Have a seat.

248
00:17:05,910 --> 00:17:06,550
Mom.

249
00:17:08,810 --> 00:17:10,250
