Mr. Zhou.

252
00:17:16,700 --> 00:17:18,829
My mom suddenly came to Sucheng for me.

253
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:21,420
Go see her.

254
00:17:22,190 --> 00:17:23,119
Thank you, boss.

255
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:32,590
I didn't expect this street to be so bustling like it used to be.

256
00:17:32,590 --> 00:17:33,590
I really miss it.

257
00:17:34,130 --> 00:17:35,470
It's been a long time.

258
00:17:36,380 --> 00:17:39,100
I remember you liked to sit in that corner

259
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:42,200
