00:19:17,570 --> 00:19:18,840
Thank you, big brother.

302
00:19:18,840 --> 00:19:20,370
Do you remember what I said?

303
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:21,320
Go.

304
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:35,870
His phone keeps ringing.

305
00:19:35,870 --> 00:19:37,600
Is there something important?

306
00:19:42,180 --> 00:19:43,060
Where are you?

307
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,310
I miss you.

308
00:20:00,830 --> 00:20:02,490
Someone called you.

309
00:20:09,450 --> 00:20:11,110
Aren't you going to call back?

310
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:14,240
It's okay.

311
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:16,030
It's nothing important.

312
00:20:22,110 --> 00:20:22,690
[WW]

313
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:32,030
That's right.

314
00:20:33,060 --> 00:20:34,900
I can arrange some work for him.

315
00:20:48,910 --> 00:20:50,310
Okay, I'll be right back.

316
00:20:54,150 --> 00:20:55,480
Do you have other plans?

317
00:20:56,120 --> 00:20:57,580
Let me take you home first.

318
00:20:58,710 --> 00:20:59,290
No need.

319
00:20:59,310 --> 00:21:00,790
You've ordered food, haven't you?

320
00:21:00,790 --> 00:21:03,130
I haven't had barbecue here for a long time.

321
00:21:03,130 --> 00:21:03,770
Just go.

322
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:04,800
I'll be fine.

323
00:21:07,230 --> 00:21:08,080
I'm sorry.

324
00:21:08,790 --> 00:21:10,730
My company called me for an emergency.

325
00:21:10,730 --> 00:21:12,790
I'll treat you to a big meal next time.

326
00:21:14,100 --> 00:21:14,870
Well,

327
00:21:14,900 --> 00:21:15,700
