328
00:21:29,810 --> 00:21:31,280
Here's the barbecue you ordered.

329
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:31,840
Sir,

330
00:21:31,910 --> 00:21:33,110
I'd also like 2 beers.

331
00:21:33,240 --> 00:21:34,240
