333
00:21:36,740 --> 00:21:37,470
Two beers.

334
00:21:37,490 --> 00:21:38,090
One beer.

335
00:21:38,120 --> 00:21:38,870
Two.

336
00:21:39,390 --> 00:21:40,190
No problem.

337
00:21:42,080 --> 00:21:43,280
Are you following me?

338
00:21:43,390 --> 00:21:44,590
I was just passing by.

339
00:21:45,190 --> 00:21:45,950
Passing by?

340
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:49,430
Does a master like you also eat barbecue on the street?

341
00:21:49,430 --> 00:21:50,480
Why can't I?

342
00:21:51,390 --> 00:21:52,830
It's the weekend.

343
00:21:52,950 --> 00:21:54,190
It's legal holiday.

344
00:21:54,430 --> 00:21:55,460
Even if I'm your contractual fiancée,

345
00:21:55,460 --> 00:21:56,900
I still have the right to take a day off, right?

346
00:21:56,900 --> 00:21:57,790
Even on legal holidays,

347
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:59,640
I can still decide who you can be with.

348
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:01,550
What's wrong with spending the weekend with my friend?

349
00:22:01,550 --> 00:22:02,280
Your friend?

350
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,840
Just a friend?

351
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:09,800
It's none of your business.

352
00:22:10,870 --> 00:22:12,470
It's written clearly in the contract

353
00:22:12,470 --> 00:22:14,190
that you have no right to interfere my plans

354
00:22:14,190 --> 00:22:15,390
for legal holidays.

355
00:22:15,430 --> 00:22:17,160
I'm not interfering your plans.

356
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:18,230
You're not?

357
00:22:18,840 --> 00:22:19,960
With so many shops

358
00:22:20,060 --> 00:22:20,670
and seats,

359
00:22:20,670 --> 00:22:21,510
do you have to sit in front of me?

360
00:22:21,510 --> 00:22:23,240
If you can sit here, why can't I?

361
00:22:24,600 --> 00:22:25,590
Your beers.

362
00:22:27,710 --> 00:22:28,510
Please enjoy.

363
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:41,340
Get your hands off it.

364
00:22:41,340 --> 00:22:45,270
-Don’t you remember the last time you were drunk at my house?
-I forgot.

365
00:22:48,950 --> 00:22:49,390
Sir,

366
00:22:49,390 --> 00:22:50,250
two more beers.

367
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:51,310
Okay.

368
00:23:08,500 --> 00:23:09,630
What are you doing?

369
00:23:09,630 --> 00:23:10,560
It's written in the contract.

370
00:23:10,560 --> 00:23:11,270
Even if it is,

371
00:23:11,270 --> 00:23:13,870
I won't let you take off your clothes in public.

372
00:23:22,730 --> 00:23:24,410
He seems to have a girlfriend.

373
00:23:26,040 --> 00:23:27,490
He left me alone.

374
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:12,240
It's hot.

375
00:24:18,150 --> 00:24:19,080
So comfortable.

376
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:24,360
You know what?

377
00:25:25,510 --> 00:25:26,710
Yu is actually good at

378
00:25:26,710 --> 00:25:28,170
running business, right?

379
00:25:30,550 --> 00:25:31,990
Like father, like son.

380
00:25:33,430 --> 00:25:34,390
That's true.

381
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:36,710
I've made up my mind.

382
00:25:37,390 --> 00:25:39,030
If Dream City runs well,

383
00:25:39,570 --> 00:25:40,450
I want to

384
00:25:40,660 --> 00:25:42,460
give him the resort project too.

385
00:25:43,060 --> 00:25:44,350
Let's see what surprise

386
00:25:44,350 --> 00:25:45,940
Yu can give me.

387
00:26:00,780 --> 00:26:01,840
What's the matter?

388
00:26:02,630 --> 00:26:04,090
Who were you with tonight?

389
00:26:10,900 --> 00:26:13,900
I had dinner with some colleagues from my department.

390
00:26:41,510 --> 00:26:43,190
Who were you really with?

391
00:26:46,890 --> 00:26:48,220
I never could lie to you.

392
00:26:53,150 --> 00:26:54,750
I went to see Su Qing tonight.

393
00:26:56,940 --> 00:26:58,400
Zhou Yu is too suspicious,

394
00:26:59,080 --> 00:27:00,140
so I thought what if I could get some important information

395
00:27:00,140 --> 00:27:01,500
from Su Qing?

396
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:03,680
Then why did you lie to me?

397
00:27:04,120 --> 00:27:05,290
Because Su Qing

398
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:07,760
didn't provide any useful information.

399
00:27:16,280 --> 00:27:19,010
I didn't expect you to be jealous because of this.

400
00:27:20,010 --> 00:27:20,810
I'm sorry.

401
00:27:29,090 --> 00:27:32,290
Zhou Mingde is going to give the resort project to Zhou Yu.

402
00:27:32,380 --> 00:27:34,380
I’ve worked so hard these years.

403
00:27:34,830 --> 00:27:35,670
In the end,

404
00:27:35,970 --> 00:27:38,830
his beloved son is going to take everything from me.

405
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:43,000
Don't worry,

406
00:27:43,450 --> 00:27:44,250
I have an idea.

407
00:27:46,510 --> 00:27:49,520
Huang Yonghua, the vice president of Dream City Department Store,

408
00:27:49,520 --> 00:27:51,780
must have benefited a lot over the years.

409
00:27:52,150 --> 00:27:54,550
If his transactions are exposed,

410
00:27:55,370 --> 00:27:56,970
the account of Dream City

411
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,480
will be investigated too.

412
00:27:59,890 --> 00:28:02,690
Huang Yonghua has worked for Zhou Mingde for more than 10 years,

413
00:28:02,690 --> 00:28:04,620
so he won't escalate the incident.

414
00:28:06,850 --> 00:28:08,970
We don't need to escalate it.

415
00:28:09,510 --> 00:28:12,240
We just need someone to investigate the account.

416
00:28:12,900 --> 00:28:14,500
As long as investigation continues,

417
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:17,250
the money on the account will remain frozen.

418
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:20,160
Three months will pass in a blink of an eye.

419
00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:22,400
If Zhou Yu has no money,

420
00:28:23,570 --> 00:28:24,500
what can he do?

421
00:28:35,140 --> 00:28:36,330
Is there really nothing going on

422
00:28:36,330 --> 00:28:37,660
between you and Su Qing?

423
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:41,260
You're the only one

424
00:28:41,340 --> 00:28:42,180
in my heart.

425
00:28:52,360 --> 00:28:52,800
What?

426
00:28:52,840 --> 00:28:53,900
False accounting?

427
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:54,530
Yes.

428
00:29:00,300 --> 00:29:01,490
Why would someone find out

429
00:29:01,490 --> 00:29:03,150
that we have false accounting

430
00:29:03,610 --> 00:29:05,380
precisely at this critical moment?

431
00:29:05,380 --> 00:29:06,510
I don't know either.

432
00:29:06,760 --> 00:29:08,440
To cooperate with the investigation,

433
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:10,760
all funds of Dream City have been frozen.

434
00:29:11,030 --> 00:29:13,330
We won't be able to carry out the following events.

435
00:29:13,330 --> 00:29:14,440
If this continues,

436
00:29:14,770 --> 00:29:17,430
I'm afraid it will affect this quarter's sales.

437
00:29:20,680 --> 00:29:22,400
Bring me all the details.

438
00:29:23,230 --> 00:29:23,760
Yes, sir.

439
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:45,660
I have something to do.

440
00:29:45,660 --> 00:29:46,720
You should go home.

441
00:29:47,170 --> 00:29:49,430
It's about the false accounting, right?

442
00:29:52,780 --> 00:29:54,160
Don't look at me like that.

443
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:55,730
If there's only one thing our employees are good at,

444
00:29:55,730 --> 00:29:57,870
it will be gossiping at the fastest speed.

445
00:29:57,870 --> 00:29:58,770
It's none of your business.

446
00:29:58,770 --> 00:29:59,770
Get out of the car.

447
00:30:01,120 --> 00:30:02,670
I heard the account involved

448
00:30:02,670 --> 00:30:04,930
the rental contract of Snapdragon Farm.

449
00:30:05,470 --> 00:30:06,230
Don't worry,

450
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:07,630
I can take care of myself.

451
00:30:08,910 --> 00:30:10,900
