452
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:12,540
I can do it in my own way.

453
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:18,800
Let's go.

454
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,510
Is this the company Huang Yonghua used

455
00:30:26,510 --> 00:30:27,890
