456
00:30:28,850 --> 00:30:31,780
It was established with Zhou's Group's investment.

457
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:34,800
Since Huang Yonghua dared to cook the books so evidently,

458
00:30:34,800 --> 00:30:36,520
