459
00:30:36,550 --> 00:30:37,680
Huang Yonghua signed many contracts

460
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:39,750
via the subsidiary of this company.

461
00:30:39,780 --> 00:30:41,430
If we want to find solid evidence,

462
00:30:41,430 --> 00:30:43,270
we can't alert him.

463
00:30:45,070 --> 00:30:46,800
Why do you have the access card?

464
00:30:47,900 --> 00:30:49,920
Are you here to help or perform a play?

465
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:50,840
Get in.

466
00:30:58,900 --> 00:30:59,490
Captain,

467
00:30:59,930 --> 00:31:01,990
two people sneaked into our company.

468
00:31:03,470 --> 00:31:04,750
Yes, sir.

469
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:06,120
