473
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,960
The evidence must be among them.

474
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:20,880
Okay.

475
00:31:36,630 --> 00:31:37,430
I found it.

476
00:31:40,750 --> 00:31:41,520
Great.

477
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,040
That's it.

478
00:31:48,350 --> 00:31:49,480
I'll leave it to you.

479
00:32:05,540 --> 00:32:06,580
How could it be?

480
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:15,350
Oh no.

481
00:32:15,390 --> 00:32:16,420
