482
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:16,730
Hurry up!

483
00:32:16,730 --> 00:32:17,470
Protect the evidence!

484
00:32:17,470 --> 00:32:18,010
Let's go!

485
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:24,600
