00:33:56,760 --> 00:33:57,420
Go get them!

505
00:34:10,429 --> 00:34:11,590
Stop! Stop!

506
00:34:14,860 --> 00:34:15,670
Stop!

507
00:34:18,500 --> 00:34:19,790
Stop! Stop!

508
00:34:19,810 --> 00:34:20,610
Stop running!

509
00:34:26,770 --> 00:34:27,420
You two

